       _M_l_a_b_e_l  displays the current volume label, if present, and
       prompts the user for a new volume  label.   To  delete  an
       existing volume label, press return at the prompt.

       _M_l_a_b_e_l will allow the following command line option:

       vv      Verbose  mode.  Display the new volume label if the
